                Sir Nicholas Grattan-Doyle
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c29b004a-3b1c-41a2-9daa-cd310888c441" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
