<p class="">I know that the hon. Member's spiritual home is Rome and that anything supported by Rome is supported by him, even stories of Barcelona.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d9b4699a-19ce-4c6c-a562-5675a16cedd8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
