<p class="">I did not mean to waste the time of the House but I am challenged. Anybody who has spent part of his life, as I have and other Members of this House have, living in towns which were shelled and having seen towns burned, cannot possibly mistake the effect of explosives and burning. You cannot have explosives <span id="108" class="column-number" data-column-number="108"></span> without a splatter. But I do not want to waste the time of the House with details.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
