            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-8609c9d0-5b6e-4216-a9fb-d9f61c384b69">
                Mr. R. Acland
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8609c9d0-5b6e-4216-a9fb-d9f61c384b69" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
