                Sir A. Sinclair
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-669c4ef9-d2ff-490d-b3b7-3178e6c0d78d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
