<p class="">I repeat that nobody knows how many there are on either side. The first thing to do is to ascertain the numbers, and if they can be ascertained by an international Commission, as is proposed, then the proposal is that the withdrawals shall be in the proportion of those numbers as found on the two sides.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
